{"tid":1500459,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵要人!!!","createTime":"2019-08-24T04:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T05:11:23.000Z","uid":102516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"752419f98785f13b0d5e3b2963638e232edae04d","tid":1500459,"uid":102516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:35:38.000Z","msg":"因應以下港鐵公告, 香港市民有權利及義務向全港最大型之公共運輸機構反映意見, 此post分為港鐵公告、港鐵中指以及行動篇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>港鐵公告篇</strong></span> , 唔想睇可跳落下面行動篇<br />\n因應觀塘區有公眾活動進行，為審慎起見，觀塘綫列車服務已作出調整，以保障乘客及員工的安全，直至另行通知<br />\n<br />\n此訊息發放時間 : 2019-08-24 12:07<br />\n<br />\n觀塘綫服務更改如下<br />\n黃埔站 往返 彩虹站：維持正常列車服務<br />\n九龍灣 往返 藍田各站：車站已經暫時關閉<br />\n彩虹站 往返 調景嶺站：暫停列車服務，請考慮使用其他交通工具<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>中指篇</strong></span> ,tldr可跳落下面行動篇, send信可以copy之後補頭尾<br />\n我們的宗旨<br />\n我們遵循可持續發展的原則&mdash;&mdash;<span style=\"color: red;\">平𧗾現世代的需要，並充分考慮與兼顧以後世代的需要</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\">本人嚴厲譴責港鐵2019.08.24觀塘線封站停駛所為, 此舉完全妄顧所有世代之需要</span><br />\n<br />\n要達致上述的承諾，我們致力：<br />\n確保為乘客提供<span style=\"color: red;\">優質及物有所值的服務：持續改善及提升</span>服務及產品質素，以滿足乘客需要。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\">本人嚴厲譴責港鐵2019.08.24觀塘線封站停駛所為, 現時之服務簡直一文不值, 質素持續降低, 無視乘客需要</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">提倡安全及遵從具道德</span>的業務操守：維護安全是對所有業務相關人士的絕對必要條件，遵從業務的道德操守。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\">本人嚴厲譴責港鐵任由警方在地鐵站內胡亂施放化學物質, 事後亦沒有徹底清理, <br />\n2019.08.24觀塘線封站停駛充分顯示港鐵有能力封站清潔, 卻對充滿有毒物質之葵芳、太古車站視若無睹 妄顧乘客安全健康 只為賺錢毫無道德</span><br />\n<br />\n港鐵以可持續發展經濟模式作為以上各點的發展基礎，讓我們能夠以負責任且可持續發展的方式實踐目標之餘，亦能夠<span style=\"color: red;\">為投資者提供合理的回報</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\">本人嚴厲譴責港鐵2019.08.24觀塘線封站停駛所為, 其損害公司聲譽及令當日車票收入大減, 令我等投資者蒙受間接捐失</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Ref: <a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/corporate/sustainability/our_approach.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcorporate%2Fsustainability%2Four_approach.html&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLvulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=b18034eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/corporate/sustainability/our_approach.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>行動篇</strong></span><br />\n港鐵熱綫 2881 8888<br />\n辦公時間  <br />\n星期一至五 上午8時30分至下午6時<br />\n星期六 上午8時30分至下午1時 (星期日及公眾假期除外)<br />\n傳真  2795 9991<br />\n郵遞  香港郵政總局信箱9916號<br />\n網上意見 <a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/feedback.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fmain%2Ffeedback.php&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLvulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=48837614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/feedback.php</a><br />\n   記住揀&rdquo; <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">請回覆</span></span>&rdquo;, 建議使用非常用電郵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">商店租戶問回水安排/<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">顧客查詢賠償</span></strong>(e.g. 快圖美約左但冇得拎相錯失工作機會)</span><br />\n車站商店租賃：2993 8372<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">落左廣告/<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打算落廣告</span></strong>既查詢日後回水安排</span><br />\n一般廣告業務：2111 0111 (觀塘綫)<br />\n車廂電視廣告：2112 6879 (觀塘綫)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">所有站既商戶/街坊/旅客可以自行打去想查詢既地鐵站查詢詳細安排<br />\n(e.g.<br />\n鄰近商戶: 因顧客減少而損失 (已預約服務而未能如期到底/站口附近依靠人流)<br />\n乘客, 特別係月票假日乘客/旅客: 有冇接駁巴士, 車費點計, 潛在損失)</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fmain%2Fcontact_us.html&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLvulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=9e8ec359\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/contact_us.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所有投訴或查詢 電話留太空卡/唔留, 留email講明<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">必須回覆</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPS: 熱線可能1點後收工冇人聽, 大家bookmark定平日打啦, email就照send 爆佢<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人 一陣觀塘見</strong></span><br />\n#香港加油 <br />\n<br />\n<code>大家想唔想要埋運輸署同運房局既投訴方法? 投訴佢地係一定要回覆\n</code>"},{"pid":"0a55efa4c959d15155e836aab43a8de49bf4062f","tid":1500459,"uid":102516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:37:01.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0d9c563d1e9a8b71db4e88284ab68bbb4650c9af","tid":1500459,"uid":102516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:39:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d88cd669553f022bdd518bd3c7ac4db11499cf8e","tid":1500459,"uid":102516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"39e2d81682291b639afef4cdc9f53bac6667c1c7","tid":1500459,"uid":102516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:46:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b549555af5f2b587716706afec5f101066c9e402","tid":1500459,"uid":102516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:53:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"be9f05cd3615d62508ba41098ec64eea87033ecc","tid":1500459,"uid":102516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"22dfc127a8d08afa06f7860812ba4a3a6cee2580","tid":1500459,"uid":102516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:11:23.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}